            <title>[CASSANDRA-7381] Snappy Compression does not work with PowerPC 64-bit, Little Endian</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7381</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In PowerPC 64-bit, Little Endian, CompressedRandomAccessReaderTest, CompressedInputStreamTest, and CFMetaDataTest fail due to the included snappy-java JAR missing the ppc64le native library.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Testing on Ubuntu 14.04, ppc64le.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The specific fix for Snappy-Java and adding the native library can be found at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/xerial/snappy-java/pull/67&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/xerial/snappy-java/pull/67&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
